title: Determine the Domain
text: The values of $$x$$ that can be taken are integers from of all $$x$$ in the pairs. Consider the lowest and highest $$x$$ values in these pairs.

title: Determine the Range
text: The values of $$y$$ that can be taken are from $$0$$ to $$3$$. Consider the lowest and highest $$y$$ values in these pairs.

title: One to One Functions
text: Is $$x$$ and $$y$$ one to one? Recall that a one to one function is a function in which each input value is mapped to one unique output value.
